        "Dear Sir,",
        "Hope you are doing well!",
        "I am a student in the \"Human Resources\" course at your institute. I submitted a request to enrol in the \"Communication skills\" course which will help me in my main study. Due to this, I was asked for an interview at the library in XYZ university at 11.00 am today.",
